    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in poor condition and is being sold as-is, ideally for someone looking for a project or a source of parts. The engine runs but requires significant mechanical attention, and the transmission shifts roughly. Externally, the body shows heavy wear including noticeable rust patches, several dents, and fading paint. The interior has seen better days, with torn upholstery and some non-functional electronics. It will likely require a tow or a very cautious drive to its next destination.",
