    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presented in impeccable showroom condition, this vehicle stands as a testament to meticulous ownership and exacting maintenance standards. Every detail, from the flawless exterior finish to the pristine interior appointments, reflects a standard of care that is rarely encountered in the pre-owned market. Mechanically sound and aesthetically indistinguishable from new, this offering represents a premier opportunity for the sophisticated buyer seeking uncompromising quality and performance.",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
