    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you ready to fall in love? I\u2019m parting ways with my absolute pride and joy, and let me tell you, she is a total stunner. This car looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor\u2014honestly, it\u2019s in such incredible shape, you\u2019d think it was brand new! I\u2019ve babied this ride from day one, and it drives like an absolute dream. If you\u2019re looking for a car that\u2019s basically perfect and ready for the road, this is the one for you. Come take a look, you definitely won't be disappointed!",
      "price": 44900.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 21
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This 997.1 Carrera S is an immaculate example of the naturally aspirated 3.8L flat-six powerhouse. The M97/01 engine delivers linear power with verified preventative IMS bearing and RMS upgrades, ensuring mechanical longevity. It features the desirable 6-speed manual transaxle and PASM (Porsche Active Suspension Management), providing exceptional dampening control and chassis response. The exterior retains a flawless factory depth with ceramic coating, while the underside remains free of any fluid seepage or oxidation. This is a concours-level, turnkey driver's car with optimal compression and a fully documented service history.",
